    <h2 class="cag-h2">Congo vs Timneh African Grey</h2>
    <a class="inf" href="/congo-vs-timneh-african-grey/"><img class="sec-img inf-img" src="/congo-vs-timneh-side-by-side-comparison-chart.webp" srcset="/congo-vs-timneh-side-by-side-comparison-chart-760.webp 760w, /congo-vs-timneh-side-by-side-comparison-chart.webp 1408w" sizes="(max-width:900px) 92vw, 760px" width="1408" height="768" alt="Congo vs Timneh African Grey comparison of size, tail colour, price and talking onset" loading="lazy"></a>
    <p>Choosing between a Congo and a Timneh African Grey is less about better and more about fit: the two subspecies share the same intelligence, but size, price, tail colour and talking onset all differ enough to matter.</p>
    <div class="vs-metrics">
      <div class="vs-m"><span>Size</span><b>Congo larger</b></div>
