    <h3 class="cag-h3">Nationwide Shipping and Two Delivery Tiers</h3>
    <p>Whichever grey wins your comparison leaves the aviary fully documented and travels one of two ways. <a href="/buy-african-grey-parrots-with-shipping/">Our shipping guide</a> details crate standards, timing and arrival day; on either route the full CITES, DNA, PCR and vet folder rides along. Pick a route below for local availability:</p>
